#. <section class="sutta" id="sn55.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn55.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Veḷudvāravagga"
msgstr "1. At Bamboo Gate"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn55.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Paṭhamasāriputtasutta"
msgstr "4. With Sāriputta (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.347"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.4:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā ca sāriputto āyasmā ca ānando sāvatthiyaṃ viharanti "
"jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time Venerable Sāriputta was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

msgctxt "sn55.4:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ānando sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito … pe … ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho āyasmā ānando āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then in the late afternoon, Venerable Ānanda came out of retreat … and said "
"to Sāriputta:"

msgctxt "sn55.4:1.3"
msgid ""
"“katinaṃ nu kho, āvuso sāriputta, dhammānaṃ samannāgamanahetu evamayaṃ pajā "
"bhagavatā byākatā sotāpannā avinipātadhammā niyatā sambodhiparāyaṇā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Reverend, how many things do people have to possess in order for the Buddha "
"to declare that they’re a stream-enterer, not liable to be reborn in the "
"underworld, bound for awakening?”"

msgctxt "sn55.4:1.4"
msgid ""
"“Catunnaṃ kho, āvuso, dhammānaṃ samannāgamanahetu evamayaṃ pajā bhagavatā "
"byākatā sotāpannā avinipātadhammā niyatā sambodhiparāyaṇā."
msgstr ""
"“Reverend, people have to possess four things in order for the Buddha to "
"declare that they’re a stream-enterer, not liable to be reborn in the "
"underworld, bound for awakening."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.4:2.1"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn55.4:2.2"
msgid "Idhāvuso, ariyasāvako buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti—"
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple has experiential confidence in the Buddha …"

msgctxt "sn55.4:2.3"
msgid "itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.4:2.4"
msgid "Dhamme … pe …"
msgstr "the teaching …"

msgctxt "sn55.4:2.5"
msgid "saṅghe … pe …"
msgstr "the Saṅgha …"

msgctxt "sn55.4:2.6"
msgid ""
"ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgato hoti akhaṇḍehi … pe … samādhisaṃvattanikehi."
msgstr ""
"And they have the ethical conduct loved by the noble ones … leading to "
"immersion."

msgctxt "sn55.4:2.7"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, āvuso, catunnaṃ dhammānaṃ samannāgamanahetu evamayaṃ pajā "
"bhagavatā byākatā sotāpannā avinipātadhammā niyatā sambodhiparāyaṇā”ti."
msgstr ""
"People have to possess these four things in order for the Buddha to declare "
"that they’re a stream-enterer, not liable to be reborn in the underworld, "
"bound for awakening.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.4:2.8"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
